{"tid":1867883,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"理性討論，醫護罷工失敗的原因","createTime":"2020-02-07T10:36:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T11:08:51.000Z","uid":2429,"like":11,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"18c6f107fa946c7324ab62410fa798c8daad1c63","tid":1867883,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:36:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">廢囉戇鳩！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一開波就自揭底牌會復工，唔輸就無天理啦！仲要成班係到打飛機話唔屌得，使唔使畀啲掌聲自己呀？依家好多機會救香港呀？要玩幾多次小組討論畀你哋慢慢試呀？仲話自己精英幾多條A，兒燈都不如呀！好好反省吓啦！垃圾！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wb5n3jL.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwb5n3jL.gif&h=67f25a89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A77MO2C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA77MO2C.jpg&h=460bb33c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OTqXb0P.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOTqXb0P.gif&h=31e53dd3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"54274ea84334a3bebcca76bb4411d51a3b780334","tid":1867883,"uid":49336,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:38:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港人就係唔夠無賴"},{"pid":"49b31fedd42ff1b349e6a7d11256147487062d87","tid":1867883,"uid":107577,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:39:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>即使醫護唔繼續罷<br />\n佢地都係成功！<br />\n<br />\n唔罷 唔等於 失敗<br />\n如果一陣投票結果係唔繼續<br />\n都唔可以 spin 到係失敗<br />\n記住,大家要既係士氣<br />\n連 HA 工會都自認失敗，咁就咬住食。<br />\n重申,唔繼續罷 不等於 失敗<br />\n<br />\n係政府同 HA 不聽訴求 專制橫蠻<br />\n<br />\n記者會同會員大會做個小總結<br />\n講大家成功做咗 d 咩<br />\n增加士氣<br />\n唔好淨係 FOCUS 政府冇做 d 咩先。<br />\neg<br />\n- 有幾多人參加咗工會<br />\n- 呢幾日有幾多人罷工<br />\n- 令到政府由唔封關，到局部封關（但仍唔足夠），都係醫護罷工所 做到既其中一個成果<br />\n- 令大家長遠關注同監察 HA 資源問題，對 HA, 醫護，病人都係好事<br />\n</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gLrYQB4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgLrYQB4.jpg&h=f72ededb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6SwmOoL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6SwmOoL.png&h=96bc9ec5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c5b4ca7d2fe8836608c0d881cd8c6a22e4bbc37c","tid":1867883,"uid":121069,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:42:29.000Z","msg":"因為佢地想做醫奴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97dbdbd2045f3cc6d7e5ef51f46f6d051e195877","tid":1867883,"uid":146030,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:45:20.000Z","msg":"佢哋真係好垃圾"},{"pid":"6dff692aadeca7f5d0ddc3687cfe8b7078aa2b9f","tid":1867883,"uid":17244,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c5b4ca7d2fe8836608c0d881cd8c6a22e4bbc37c","tid":1867883,"uid":121069,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:42:29.000Z","msg":"因為佢地想做醫奴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:45:38.000Z","msg":"原來香港只係屬於20000名醫護人員<br />\n<br />\n感謝醫護<br />\n<br />\n不完美，可接受，有改善空間"},{"pid":"c632c66e9c7d20366b174102fb115b448385b288","tid":1867883,"uid":159876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54274ea84334a3bebcca76bb4411d51a3b780334","tid":1867883,"uid":49336,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:38:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港人就係唔夠無賴"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:46:33.000Z","msg":"呢句都係打飛機既說話。唔好逃避現實。<br />\n係廢呀！廢呀！無其他形容詞，係廢！"},{"pid":"da3bdaba2eef4c8f26d6dbb7eae92a255873c0cb","tid":1867883,"uid":158889,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"cited